1
00:00:03,320 --> 00:00:09,660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Hey!! It's just like sweeet magic!! Aha!</i></font>

2
00:00:12,450 --> 00:00:15,200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Hi, it's me! 
The one with that killer smile!</i></font>

3
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:17,460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Stealing your gaze with a shocking style!</i></font>

4
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:18,580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Smooth as ever, I escort you</i></font>

5
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:20,040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>And this voice, seducing you</i></font>

6
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:22,790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Ah, come on, let's dance; 
I'm aiming straight for your heart</i></font>

7
00:00:23,310 --> 00:00:25,960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>I am your ace darlin'</i></font>

8
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:28,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Confidence? Yeah, I've got plenty</i></font>

9
00:00:28,550 --> 00:00:29,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Please Please</i></font>

10
00:00:29,550 --> 00:00:33,180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Whisper just to me, call my name</i></font>

11
00:00:33,180 --> 00:00:38,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>You're too popular, 
it drives me crazy and I'm not okay</i></font>

12
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:41,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>But I'm sorry, losing's not my thing</i></font>

13
00:00:41,850 --> 00:00:42,770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Hey, girl</i></font>

14
00:00:42,770 --> 00:00:43,770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Look this way!</i></font>

15
00:00:43,770 --> 00:00:46,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>I see your smile, smile, smile, 
 I wanna make it all mine</i></font>

16
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:49,950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Crash, crash, crash, 
our special connection shines</i></font>

17
00:00:49,950 --> 00:00:54,200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Dance, dance, 
our world is non-stop groovin'</i></font>

18
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:56,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>I'll show you my perfect 
A-side, side, side</i></font>

19
00:00:56,870 --> 00:01:00,540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>And my private B-side, side, side; 
I'll show you everything</i></font>

20
00:01:00,540 --> 00:01:04,210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>So take my hand and let's roll</i></font>

21
00:01:04,210 --> 00:01:06,340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Sweet Sweet Sweet magic!!</i></font>

22
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:10,760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Sweetie honey Sweetie honey</i></font>

23
00:01:13,820 --> 00:01:16,310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Sweetie honey Sweetie honey</i></font>

24
00:01:16,310 --> 00:01:19,180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>It's a spell that makes your heart race</i></font>

25
00:01:19,180 --> 00:01:21,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>We can't go back</i></font>

26
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:24,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>You're falling in love with me, c'mon!</i></font>

27
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:25,540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Sweetie honey</i></font>

28
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:27,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Sweet Sweet Sweet magic!!</i></font>

29
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<b><font face="Verdana"><font color="#fff9fa"><font size="22">Is It <font color="#fafafa">Really Okay For Me to Be Here?</font></font></font></font></b></font>

30
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Last time, during my job...</i></font>

31
00:01:37,660 --> 00:01:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say that line again.</font>

32
00:01:39,290 --> 00:01:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't give Tamon-kun 
what he asked for, and as a result...</i></font>

33
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you really do think 
I'm creepy, don't you?!</font>

34
00:01:46,110 --> 00:01:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That happened... and now we're here.</i></font>

35
00:01:46,790 --> 00:01:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#666767">Oversized Garbage</font></font></font>

36
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fukuhara-sama.</font>

37
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek!</font>

38
00:01:51,690 --> 00:01:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing Tamon-kun is allowed to 
throw away is his lack of confidence!</font>

39
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="26"><font color="#666767">Oversized Garbage</font></font></font>

40
00:01:57,470 --> 00:02:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seeing you act so normally somehow made me
 want to be thrown away even more.</font>

41
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm begging you, please don't let one
 mere fan's behavior affect you so much!</font>

42
00:02:07,610 --> 00:02:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't say "mere fan." 
All of my fans are very important to me!</font>

43
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Squee.</i></font>

44
00:02:11,690 --> 00:02:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#d66484">Squee</font></b></font>

45
00:02:13,100 --> 00:02:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I'm going on and on
about myself again.</font>

46
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

47
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-san, are you doing okay today?</font>

48
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am.</font>

49
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

50
00:02:23,330 --> 00:02:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Squee.</i></font>

51
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#d66484"><font size="30">Squee</font></font></b></font>

52
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Calm down... whatever this is!</i></font>

53
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like everything you say 
is correct, Kinoshita-san.</font>

54
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell that you're trying 
to keep your distance for my sake, too.</font>

55
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even then...</font>

56
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Keep the distance!</i></font>

57
00:02:43,020 --> 00:02:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel a bit lonely.</font>

58
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you're the closest person 
to me right now, Kinoshita-san.</font>

59
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter what, I'm just a fan.</i></font>

60
00:02:56,890 --> 00:02:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The most important thing to me 
is Tamon-kun's dream.</i></font>

61
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if he tells me he's lonely,</i></font>

62
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't just go, "Okay, I understand," 
and change how I feel.</i></font>

63
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know what to do.</i></font>

64
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give me some time.</font>

65
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

66
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, I just...</font>

67
00:03:15,790 --> 00:03:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not exactly sure what I should do.</font>

68
00:03:18,330 --> 00:03:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't even really know 
what I'm thinking,</font>

69
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:25,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I don't want to casually say anything
 while I'm still trying to figure it out.</font>

70
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's no use.</i></font>

71
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's the me who reveres 
Tamon-kun as a god...</i></font>

72
00:03:34,770 --> 00:03:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the me who's realized that 
he's the closest to me right now.</i></font>

73
00:03:40,410 --> 00:03:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I'm currently straddling the line
between the two.</i></font>

74
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

75
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I realized that I didn't know you 
at all, Kinoshita-san.</font>

76
00:03:56,190 --> 00:04:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... I wanted to know more about you 
and ended up coming on too strong again.</font>

77
00:04:02,730 --> 00:04:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry that I ignored
 your feelings, Kinoshita-san.</font>

78
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll wait for you.</font>

79
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd really hurt if you hated me, 
Kinoshita-san.</font>

80
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you two datin' or what?</font>

81
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki-kun. How long have you been here?</font>

82
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somewhere around it'd be okay 
to throw you away or whatever.</font>

83
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, I see.</font>

84
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So he basically heard </i>everything<i>!</i></font>

85
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad, my dude. 
You guys been together long?</font>

86
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For about three months.</font>

87
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! That's how long 
I've been his housekeeper!</font>

88
00:04:34,850 --> 00:04:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't tell anyone.</font>

89
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, really! You've got the wrong idea!</font>

90
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brings you here today?</font>

91
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They turned off my power,
 so let me hang out here.</font>

92
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font size="30"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#b82440">Didn't Pay</font></font></font></b></font>

93
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? You didn't pay?!</i></font>

94
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The agency pays for our rent,
 but utilities are on us, so you know...</font>

95
00:04:49,610 --> 00:04:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"So you know"?</font>

96
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:57,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't you going to work?</font>

97
00:04:57,110 --> 00:05:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I guess you had to 
see somethin' weird earlier.</font>

98
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can just forget all about that.</font>

99
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right...</font>

100
00:05:02,710 --> 00:05:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something weird?</font>

101
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ishibashi-san was mistaken 
for a creeper near my school.</font>

102
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Really?!</font>

103
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. 
It didn't turn into a big deal.</font>

104
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So Natsuki-kun's ex-girlfriend 
is Asuka-sensei...</i></font>

105
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she was acting really weird.</i></font>

106
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotta jot this down...</font>

107
00:05:34,970 --> 00:05:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rare sneak peek of him writing a song!</font>

108
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my first time seeing it, too.</font>

109
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so cool...</font>

110
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wake up!</font>

111
00:05:46,490 --> 00:05:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't wanna. I'm tired. This sucks.</font>

112
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about the song?</font>

113
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll get done. It'll get done real soon.</font>

114
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wake up!</font>

115
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sense a negative aura 
different from Gloomyhara-san's.</i></font>

116
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna write it instead? You could 
pull it off with yer rarin'-to-go persona.</font>

117
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never even managed 
to rip toilet paper on the lines!</font>

118
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I ever pull off writing a song?!</font>

119
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, but are you interested?</font>

120
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I can't say that I'm not... 
I do love music, after all.</font>

121
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see, I see. 
Writin' songs is pretty great.</font>

122
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't very convincing.</font>

123
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention, 
why did you run away again?</font>

124
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were finally motivated.</font>

125
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, well, you know.</font>

126
00:06:27,010 --> 00:06:28,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just felt like...</font>

127
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I stole someone's life, so I probably 
shouldn't be writin' an anthem.</font>

128
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

129
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ya see, my ex-girlfriend...</font>

130
00:06:42,850 --> 00:06:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name's Asuka, 
and I destroyed her life once.</font>

131
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Man, this sucks.</i></font>

132
00:06:54,970 --> 00:06:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's cold today, so if I fall asleep 
like this, I might just freeze to death.</i></font>

133
00:06:59,350 --> 00:07:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, it's not like I have anything 
I wanna do in life, so whatever.</i></font>

134
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. I brought you a tip!</font>

135
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want some dak-galbi instead.</font>

136
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit your whinin'!</font>

137
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just a dumb middle schooler.
 Go back home already.</font>

138
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not like my parents
 are around even if I did.</font>

139
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where've you been sleepin'?</font>

140
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty much at a friend's place 
or a manga café and such.</font>

141
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And such?! 
What are you doin' about money?</font>

142
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This.</font>

143
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank ya.</font>

144
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Lemme sing a song.</font>

145
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My parents had zero interest in me.</i></font>

146
00:07:44,370 --> 00:07:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It didn't matter what I did 
or how hard I worked.</i></font>

147
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They never paid any attention to me.</i></font>

148
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which is why I ended up sucking 
at working hard at anything.</i></font>

149
00:07:53,580 --> 00:07:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's got such a cute face.</font>

150
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}For real. He looks like a girl.</font>

151
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asuka was two grades above me 
and in high school.</i></font>

152
00:07:57,650 --> 00:07:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm so jealous!</font>

153
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She'd always bring me takoyaki 
instead of some loose change.</i></font>

154
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's your tip.</font>

155
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you keep comin' 'round every night?</font>

156
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You like me or somethin'?</font>

157
00:08:07,650 --> 00:08:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a chance. 
You're gloomy, irresponsible,</font>

158
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they say you're a looker, 
but I prefer guys with softer features.</font>

159
00:08:12,930 --> 00:08:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I do like your songs.</font>

160
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, for all your complainin', 
you are waitin' around for me every night.</font>

161
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you like me?</font>

162
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

163
00:08:25,490 --> 00:08:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You nag too much 
and can't mind your own business.</font>

164
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Then gimme back that takoyaki!</font>

165
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh.</font>

166
00:08:30,730 --> 00:08:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

167
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the fact that you work 
so hard is pretty cool.</font>

168
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't do that.</font>

169
00:08:41,250 --> 00:08:43,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#454846"><font size="26">Osaka High School
Judo Tournament</font></font></b></font>

170
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We were complete opposites, 
but we somehow got along great.</i></font>

171
00:08:48,940 --> 00:08:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But don't you wanna become a singer?</font>

172
00:08:52,140 --> 00:08:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I do like music, but I was 
just doin' that stuff to make money.</font>

173
00:08:57,210 --> 00:08:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Becomin' a singer is pretty impossible.</font>

174
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only a small fraction 
of people ever succeed.</font>

175
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f6f4f6">Takoyaki               Kodama</font></font></b></font>

176
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#ededf1">Takoyaki</font></font></b></font>

177
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you gonna do 
after you graduate middle school?</font>

178
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll probably find a random job.</font>

179
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you can just work at our shop.</font>

180
00:09:10,540 --> 00:09:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad!</font>

181
00:09:11,490 --> 00:09:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just thinkin' 'bout 
puttin' a listing out.</font>

182
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd love to have ya, Natsuki-kun.</font>

183
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this?</font>

184
00:09:19,540 --> 00:09:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, good job.</font>

185
00:09:21,050 --> 00:09:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad!</font>

186
00:09:24,730 --> 00:09:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you waiting!</font>

187
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a cute face, sonny.</font>

188
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home! 
Can I get an order of cheese yaki?</font>

189
00:09:31,010 --> 00:09:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#454846"><font size="26">Kansai High School
Judo Tournament</font></font></b></font>

190
00:09:34,970 --> 00:09:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great job, Asuka!</font>

191
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it!</font>

192
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might just think of me 
as a younger brother,</font>

193
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I don't see you as a sibling.</font>

194
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to be my girlfriend.</font>

195
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#2ef1e5">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

196
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font size="10"><font face="Arial"><font color="#e2ffff">Received Messages</font></font></font></b></font>

197
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

198
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font size="20"><font color="#1a0f19">After careful consideration,
we regret to inform you
that you have not been selected.



The names of the participants
who passed the audition
will be listed on our
homepage on 6/25.</font></font></b></font>

199
00:10:09,170 --> 00:10:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd it go?</font>

200
00:10:09,170 --> 00:10:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f6f4f6">Takoyaki               Kodama</font></font></b></font>

201
00:10:09,170 --> 00:10:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#ededf1">Takoyaki</font></font></b></font>

202
00:10:10,310 --> 00:10:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I failed again.</font>

203
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's always next time!</font>

204
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit treatin' me like a kid! 
How'd it go for you?</font>

205
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heh. I got through the Kansai Tournament!</font>

206
00:10:19,850 --> 00:10:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh!</font>

207
00:10:21,170 --> 00:10:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're gonna have a feast!</font>

208
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that your song, Natsuki-kun?</font>

209
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no. It's just a cover.</font>

210
00:10:33,730 --> 00:10:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, when I win the inter-high, 
sing me an original song.</font>

211
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, though?</font>

212
00:10:39,210 --> 00:10:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you said you wanted to 
try writin' songs!</font>

213
00:10:41,570 --> 00:10:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, please?</font>

214
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, I definitely wanna hear that!</font>

215
00:10:44,330 --> 00:10:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We wanna hear! We wanna hear!</font>

216
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I guess.</font>

217
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I'll work a bit harder, too.</font>

218
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I was with Asuka,</i></font>

219
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I naturally wanted to give my all 
doing something, too.</i></font>

220
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

221
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="26"><font color="#1a0f19">{\an8}After careful consideration, it has been decided
 that you will be moving onto the final round.</font></font></b></font>

222
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

223
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#1a0f19">{\an8}<font size="40">final round</font></font></b></font>

224
00:11:08,690 --> 00:11:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heck yeah!</font>

225
00:11:09,570 --> 00:11:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! This is amazing, Natsuki!</font>

226
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally saved up some money, so I'll be 
able to buy Asuka a birthday present.</font>

227
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki.</font>

228
00:11:21,830 --> 00:11:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad...</font>

229
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How've you been?</font>

230
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you doin' here?</font>

231
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm doin' an audition right now, 
and things are goin' well.</font>

232
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next week is the final—</font>

233
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about money?</font>

234
00:11:34,630 --> 00:11:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're workin', aren't ya? 
You need to pay your family back.</font>

235
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're absolute trash.</font>

236
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell do you think 
you're talkin' to, huh?!</font>

237
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't! That's...</font>

238
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for Asuka—</font>

239
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay, Natsuki?!</font>

240
00:11:53,210 --> 00:11:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Asu...</font>

241
00:11:54,530 --> 00:11:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hurt at all?</font>

242
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?!</font>

243
00:11:57,170 --> 00:11:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You little...</font>

244
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:09,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asuka!</font>

245
00:12:11,050 --> 00:12:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We bring you the girls' team matches</i></font>

246
00:12:14,950 --> 00:12:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}of the National High School 
Judo Tournament today.</i></font>

247
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The semi-final is about to start.</i></font>

248
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}There was also a promising athlete
 who had to withdraw due to injury...</i></font>

249
00:12:24,370 --> 00:12:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asuka...</font>

250
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you came to visit me, Natsuki?</font>

251
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

252
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm totally fine! Just look at me!</font>

253
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all my fault...</font>

254
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, how'd the audition go?</font>

255
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The final round was yesterday, wasn't it?</font>

256
00:12:37,420 --> 00:12:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been curious since you didn't contac—</font>

257
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't go.</font>

258
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

259
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How the hell was I supposed to go 
in this situation?</font>

260
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why...</font>

261
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell're you doin'? 
Are you stupid?!</font>

262
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, what the hell? 
This is the worst...</font>

263
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:53,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asu—</font>

264
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out!</font>

265
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't wanna to see your face.</font>

266
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After that accident,</i></font>

267
00:13:01,990 --> 00:13:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>all my motivation completely left me.</i></font>

268
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All of Asuka's hard work 
ended up for nothin'.</i></font>

269
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it was all my fault.</i></font>

270
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I quit my job at the takoyaki shop</i></font>

271
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and went back to 
the aimless life I used to live.</i></font>

272
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I cared about was
 having fun in the moment.</i></font>

273
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was just easier.</i></font>

274
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Later, I randomly did an audition 
my friend goaded me into</i></font>

275
00:13:31,850 --> 00:13:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and shockingly debuted.</i></font>

276
00:13:34,260 --> 00:13:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was happy, but honestly, 
it felt really weird.</i></font>

277
00:13:38,610 --> 00:13:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was in limbo and felt 
a bit guilty toward the fans.</i></font>

278
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font size="20"><font color="#959542">Natsuki,
<font size="14"><font color="#8f286b">throw me a kiss!</font></font></font></font></b></font>

279
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font size="18"><font color="#6d4f3a">Natsuki
<font size="14"><font color="#6e433d"><font size="20">Shoot me!</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

280
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Natsuki!</font>

281
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:46,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Show us your angel smile!</font>

282
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, everyone.</i></font>

283
00:13:45,690 --> 00:13:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I can't help but wonder...</i></font>

284
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I love you!</font>

285
00:13:47,570 --> 00:13:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>if it's really okay for me to be here.</i></font>

286
00:13:57,650 --> 00:14:00,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it really okay for me to be here?!</font>

287
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:04,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, yes. You don't have power, so sure.</font>

288
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't worry about it.</font>

289
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You drank too much, Ishibashi-san. 
Have some water—</font>

290
00:14:09,370 --> 00:14:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he fell asleep!</font>

291
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki-kun usually seems a bit cold, 
but I guess he talks a lot when he drinks.</font>

292
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:18,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He does.</font>

293
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This goes for Keito-kun, too,</font>

294
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I didn't know anything 
about Natsuki-kun either.</font>

295
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never tried to find out 
how he felt being an idol...</font>

296
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're in the same group and yet... 
I feel pretty pathetic.</font>

297
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel so pathetic that I could die.</font>

298
00:14:33,790 --> 00:14:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you not go under too, Gloomyhara-san?!</font>

299
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

300
00:14:37,620 --> 00:14:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason Natsuki-kun can't give his all
 has to do with this Asuka-san person?</font>

301
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:44,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try asking her about it, too.</font>

302
00:14:44,190 --> 00:14:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how are we supposed to do that?</font>

303
00:14:46,420 --> 00:14:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asuka-san...</font>

304
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rather, Asuka-sensei... heh.</font>

305
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She happens to be my homeroom teacher!</font>

306
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

307
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f7f6ef">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

308
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="22"><font color="#777970">Security Camera</font></font></font></font>

309
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="35"><font color="#c1322d">Beware of Suspi</font></font></font></font>

310
00:15:00,830 --> 00:15:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e6efe9">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

311
00:15:00,830 --> 00:15:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#147409"><b>Midoriyama Tailor</b></font></font></font></font>

312
00:15:01,740 --> 00:15:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That person is 
Ishibashi-san's ex-girlfriend</font>

313
00:15:04,530 --> 00:15:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and my homeroom teacher, Asuka-sensei.</font>

314
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e6efe9">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

315
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#147409"><b>Midoriyama Tailor</b></font></font></font></font>

316
00:15:07,070 --> 00:15:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

317
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f7f6ef">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

318
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="22"><font color="#777970">Security Camera</font></font></font></font>

319
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="35"><font color="#c1322d">Beware of Suspi</font></font></font></font>

320
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it's a bit late for this,</font>

321
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but should we really stick our noses
 into someone else's relationship?</font>

322
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This seems completely insensitive!</font>

323
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f1f0ec">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

324
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="6"><font color="#777970">Security Camera</font></font></font></font>

325
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="9"><font color="#c1322d">Beware of Suspicious Individuals</font></font></font></font>

326
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if I get arrested
 for sexual harassment?!</font>

327
00:15:19,610 --> 00:15:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please calm down!</font>

328
00:15:21,190 --> 00:15:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was a bit exhausted,</font>

329
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it made me really happy when 
 you noticed and said that I wasn't okay.</font>

330
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:27,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#d66484">Squee</font></b></font>

331
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some people don't like being meddled with,
 but some appreciate being cared for, too!</font>

332
00:15:33,380 --> 00:15:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't know how they feel 
until we ask them.</font>

333
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great Sage Kinoshita...</font>

334
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just have you be my friend 
from middle school!</font>

335
00:15:42,210 --> 00:15:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#d66484"><font size="20">Badump...</font></font></b></font>

336
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend!</font>

337
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Asuka-sensei!</font>

338
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a coincidence.</font>

339
00:15:50,930 --> 00:15:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-san...</font>

340
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A creeper!</font>

341
00:15:57,470 --> 00:15:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tamon-kun!</font>

342
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just push me down like that.</font>

343
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're his housekeeper?!</font>

344
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea that you actually 
knew Tamon-kun, Kinoshita-san!</font>

345
00:16:22,740 --> 00:16:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention, Tamon-kun 
in the flesh is too intense!</font>

346
00:16:25,170 --> 00:16:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to meet you.</font>

347
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He spoke!</font>

348
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to get used to 
this already, Utage.</font>

349
00:16:29,490 --> 00:16:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said my name!</font>

350
00:16:34,490 --> 00:16:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does the air around here 
taste really good?</font>

351
00:16:34,490 --> 00:16:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Whoa! Kinoshita-san?! Are you okay?!</font>

352
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, something's different.</font>

353
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kinoshita-san!</font>

354
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We wanted to talk to you about Natsuki.</font>

355
00:16:40,730 --> 00:16:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was also curious about 
what happened the other day...</font>

356
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah...</font>

357
00:16:45,310 --> 00:16:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Natsuki tell you anything?</font>

358
00:16:47,290 --> 00:16:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He mentioned that you two 
used to be a couple.</font>

359
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, well...</font>

360
00:16:52,890 --> 00:16:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

361
00:16:55,190 --> 00:16:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, Natsuki's not doing 
too well with work lately.</font>

362
00:16:58,290 --> 00:17:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why?</font>

363
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's having trouble writing the song 
he's on right now.</font>

364
00:17:03,390 --> 00:17:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said that he has no right to write 
this song since he destroyed your life.</font>

365
00:17:10,210 --> 00:17:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki said that?</font>

366
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might annoy you two that we're sticking
our necks into this private matter,</font>

367
00:17:18,330 --> 00:17:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I just couldn't leave Natsuki alone.</font>

368
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

369
00:17:24,950 --> 00:17:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

370
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:29,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, you said you 
were a Natsuki-kun oshi,</font>

371
00:17:29,700 --> 00:17:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but then the other day you 
said you didn't know him...</font>

372
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's because...</font>

373
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The world never needs to know
 about an idol's ex, right?</font>

374
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True.</font>

375
00:17:40,490 --> 00:17:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, if people found out
 he was still meeting with his ex,</font>

376
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">his career would go up in flames, right?</font>

377
00:17:46,050 --> 00:17:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet he keeps casually coming to see me! 
That idiot!</font>

378
00:17:49,150 --> 00:17:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Facts!</font>

379
00:17:50,810 --> 00:17:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, Natsuki thinks 
that you hate him, Asuka-san.</font>

380
00:17:54,250 --> 00:17:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

381
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone's hated here, it's me.</font>

382
00:18:01,530 --> 00:18:03,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I regretted what I did,</font>

383
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so when I found out Natsuki did 
another audition, it made me so happy.</font>

384
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that Natsuki?</font>

385
00:18:10,740 --> 00:18:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

386
00:18:11,530 --> 00:18:16,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be your happy, pretty angel!
 I'm Natsuki Ishibashi!</font>

387
00:18:16,740 --> 00:18:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the?!</font>

388
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This guy even found existing exhausting,</font>

389
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet he was singing and dancing 
and full of smiles.</font>

390
00:18:27,590 --> 00:18:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so proud of Natsuki.</font>

391
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I truly am.</font>

392
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I could ever hate him.</font>

393
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I love Natsuki 
when he's doing his best!</font>

394
00:18:46,780 --> 00:18:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there... any way you'd be willing 
to tell Natsuki that directly?</font>

395
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

396
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, Natsuki's a celebrity.</font>

397
00:18:57,070 --> 00:18:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He lives in a different world.</font>

398
00:18:58,860 --> 00:19:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd just be a nuisance 
if a regular ol' person went to see him.</font>

399
00:19:02,570 --> 00:19:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I understand what Sensei 
is saying so much, it hurts...</i></font>

400
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's not how Natsuki feels at all.</font>

401
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

402
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki has a ridiculous amount of talent.</font>

403
00:19:15,490 --> 00:19:18,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he drinks too much, 
he won't quit smoking at all,</font>

404
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and runs away all the time, 
meaning he has flaws, too.</font>

405
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why...</font>

406
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may think idols are amazing
 or that regular people aren't,</font>

407
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's absolutely <i>not</i> true.</font>

408
00:19:31,130 --> 00:19:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I really want to say.</font>

409
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so nice.</font>

410
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sort of surprised.</font>

411
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I totally thought you were the
 "I'm an idol, so I can do anything" type.</font>

412
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#c1b8ff"><font size="32">Gulp</font></font></b></font>

413
00:19:46,780 --> 00:19:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I say stuff like that at work,</font>

414
00:19:49,140 --> 00:19:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}but no, wait... uh... huh? 
What am I saying?</font>

415
00:19:50,510 --> 00:19:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hottiehara-kun is panicking!</i></font>

416
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This rare footage should be saved
 for future generations!</i></font>

417
00:19:56,280 --> 00:19:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's just not that easy.</font>

418
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead...</font>

419
00:20:01,530 --> 00:20:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was hoping you'd show 
something to Natsuki.</font>

420
00:20:03,610 --> 00:20:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

421
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki-kun! Please look at this account!</font>

422
00:20:10,220 --> 00:20:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, your handwriting sucks ass!</font>

