447
00:20:29,990 --> 00:20:31,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Congrats on your debut!</i></font>

448
00:20:31,690 --> 00:20:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You made it into third place 
right after Ouri-kun.</i></font>

449
00:20:33,410 --> 00:20:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been waiting 
for this day for so long.</i></font>

450
00:20:35,770 --> 00:20:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll continue supporting you!</i></font>

451
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's been closely followin' me 
ever since my audition!</font>

452
00:20:42,690 --> 00:20:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell? Why didn't she tell me?!</font>

453
00:20:44,220 --> 00:20:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd she run from me? 
This makes no sense! Hello?!</font>

