458
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#979691">I'm watching you. Get it together, already!</font></font></font></font>

459
00:21:01,230 --> 00:21:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look forward to working 
with you again today.</font>

460
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's gotten into Gloomyhara-san today?</font>

461
00:21:13,840 --> 00:21:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's like an overexcited grade schooler
 the night before his field trip.</font>

462
00:21:17,390 --> 00:21:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably because he's never gotten
 to go to a cultural festival before.</font>

463
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow...</font>

464
00:21:23,050 --> 00:21:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His high school has
 a cultural festival coming up, too?</font>

465
00:21:25,840 --> 00:21:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, I'm talkin' about the one 
at your school.</font>

466
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

467
00:21:31,190 --> 00:21:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you know, Keito's an alum
 of Hanagaya High School.</font>

468
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And F/ACE has a shoot 
at their cultural festival—</font>

469
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops. I just spilled the beans.</font>

470
00:21:41,290 --> 00:21:42,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, forget I said anything.</font>

471
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:50,790
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24" color="#c3c7c4"><b>{\an8}<font color="#68708b">Tokyo Municipal Hanagaya High School</font></b></font>

472
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:50,790
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24" color="#c3c7c4"><b>{\an8}<font color="#68708b">Tokyo Municipal Hanagaya High School</font></b></font>

473
00:21:45,530 --> 00:21:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that wraps up the outline 
for the new show, <i>"F/ACE School",</i></font>

474
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and our plans for security that day.</font>

475
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't want any chaos,</font>

476
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we hope the teachers and staff 
will help keep things under control.</font>

477
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

478
00:21:58,340 --> 00:21:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Natsuki's...</i></font>

